series_description:
This records series documents personal
information on each member of the
Wellness Center. Records may include but
are not limited to: registration forms;
waiver of liability; health assessment;
wellness prescriptions; health history;
medical clearance; and any other related
documentation or correspondence.

This records series documents the
recruitment of faculty and non-teaching
positions by UTMB. Records may include
but are not limited to: request to post;
position description; recruiting plan
(includes search committee list);
advertising; interview detail; Approval To
Interview Form (pre-interview summary);
applicants recommended for interview;
CV's for all applicants listed; and any other
related documentation or
correspondence.
